{"tid":1429574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人/藍屍最新杯葛清單","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:29:35.000Z","uid":48582,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a23c0186a8fbe6f7cf03907236c9ab3fa604e1ed","tid":1429574,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"好可惜，佢哋唔係杯葛晒成個香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCVDMvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCVDMvR.png&h=1652d249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【揭露港乱背后无良商家】&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n傳出去，等佢無得發展中國市場<br />\n撐暴徒店舖列表<br />\n(希望大家可以提供, 我地全民杯葛, 報料者請複製並加入新店舖)<br />\n<br />\n交通及旅遊界<br />\n1) 星晨旅遊<br />\n<br />\n飲食界<br />\n1) 拾味山西刀削麵 (灣仔)<br />\n2) 渣哥 (所有門市)<br />\n3) 雅翠餐廳 (屯門)<br />\n4) 無肉食<br />\n5) 蘇媽蘇媽 (荃灣及深水埗).<br />\n6) 程班長 (荔枝角)<br />\n7) 八方雲集 (TKO)<br />\n8) 渣哥一九九六<br />\n9) 賞茶（fb出post)<br />\n10) 走肉朋友<br />\n<br />\n街市<br />\n1) 協晶肉食公司 (屯門友愛街市)<br />\n<br />\n化妝品<br />\n1) Sasa<br />\n<br />\n運動<br />\n1) zen fitness studio<br />\n<br />\n雜貨<br />\n1)實惠<br />\n2)759<br />\n航運<br />\n1) 國泰，港龍<br />\n<br />\n教育<br />\n1)遵理學校<br />\n- Guy Leung&nbsp;<br />\n- Edward Fung&nbsp;<br />\n- Kenneth Lau<br />\n- Patrick Chan<br />\n- Terance Tse(TT)<br />\n2)現代教育<br />\n- Sam Chai<br />\n- Cyrus Chung<br />\n- Dick Hui<br />\n3)英皇教育<br />\n- Tsui Tsui<br />\n- Liu Tin Yan&nbsp;<br />\n- Hung Wai Kuen<br />\n- Shinno Choi<br />\n服饰类<br />\nG2000&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n/来自孤烟暮蝉&nbsp;#守护香港#&nbsp;#深水埗#&nbsp;#北角#&nbsp;<br />\n#为什么乱港派头目子女无一上街游行#</blockquote>"},{"pid":"798f74fd558f3a546c9ebf9692b890d2b7f63c0c","tid":1429574,"uid":8441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過人地想唔想入支支市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a00a3bf2b54a5fbb10737e81f3013178f27799","tid":1429574,"uid":48582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"798f74fd558f3a546c9ebf9692b890d2b7f63c0c","tid":1429574,"uid":8441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過人地想唔想入支支市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:08:57.000Z","msg":"班補習佬變撚咗店舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32266c46e7893f1b37403eb6d2f26f64dc80c223","tid":1429574,"uid":220601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"正 呢D地方無支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c1f434bb9ef62569489d77d74bcfbc6583d118","tid":1429574,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"田北辰都反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec8dafbd4051e473c889f3eeab97d0ff00aa29e","tid":1429574,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"70ac5116bb7b95a138c1a646035d0ae558c1e9f9","tid":1429574,"uid":268365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:13:18.000Z","ms